s3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">对当前来讲十分重要。<span class="_ _9"></span>然而在汉地，<span class="_ _9"></span><span class="ls13">学习佛法的场所并不多，</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ybc ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">不像我们藏地，<span class="_ _8"></span>光是我家乡炉霍县，<span class="_ _8"></span>人口只有四万左右，<span class="_ _8"></span>寺</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ybd ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">院就有二十多座；<span class="_ _7"></span>五明佛学院所在的县城叫色达，<span class="_ _7"></span>人口也不</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ybe ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">到四万，<span class="_ _9"></span><span class="ls13">但却有寺院近三十座。<span class="_ _9"></span><span class="ls12">你们去过藏地的人也都知道，</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ybf ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">在那里坐车的时候，<span class="_ _7"></span>一会儿一座佛塔，<span class="_ _7"></span>一会儿一个寺院……</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc0 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">这样的建筑数不胜数。<span class="_ _8"></span>而且，<span class="_ _8"></span>寺院大多都有讲经说法，<span class="_ _8"></span>孩子</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc1 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">们从小就住在附近，<span class="_ _7"></span>每个月受八关斋戒等，<span class="_ _7"></span>在这种环境的影</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc2 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">响下，<span class="_ _8"></span>对佛教的教理或多或少都有了解。<span class="_ _8"></span>可是在汉地，<span class="_ _8"></span>每个</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y134 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">城市的人口有几百万、<span class="_ _8"></span>甚至上千万，<span class="_ _8"></span>寺院却寥寥无几、<span class="_ _8"></span>屈指</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
